source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Conservation Elements - Terrestrial Species: Burrowing Owl
source.description: This map shows the potential current distribution of burrowing owl, in the context of current and near-term terrestrial intactness and long-term potential for climate change and energy development.
